<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<jmeterTestPlan version="1.2" properties="5.0" jmeter="5.6.3">
  <hashTree>
    <TestPlan guiclass="TestPlanGui" testclass="TestPlan" testname="Hospin Concentrated Load - Scenario B-3">
      <stringProp name="TestPlan.comments">시나리오 B-3: 집중 부하 (엔드포인트 한계 탐색)
B3-Hospital: GET /api/hospital/search (파라미터 없음) + GET /api/hospital/nearby — 50 Users, 300s
B3-Search: GET /api/hospital/search 4종 — 30 Users, 300s
실행: serialize=true (B3-Hospital 완료 후 B3-Search 시작)
CLI: jmeter -n -t scenario_b_concentrated.jmx -JTS=$(date +%Y%m%d-%H%M%S) -l /dev/null
인증 불필요 (permitAll 엔드포인트)</stringProp>
      <elementProp name="TestPlan.user_defined_variables" elementType="Arguments" guiclass="ArgumentsPanel" testclass="Arguments" testname="User Defined Variables">
        <collectionProp name="Arguments.arguments"/>
      </elementProp>
      <boolProp name="TestPlan.functional_mode">false</boolProp>
      <boolProp name="TestPlan.serialize_threadgroups">true</boolProp>
    </TestPlan>
    <hashTree>
      <SetupThreadGroup guiclass="SetupThreadGroupGui" testclass="SetupThreadGroup" testname="setUp Thread Group">
        <stringProp name="TestPlan.comments">TS 타임스탬프 초기화. CLI 미전달 시 현재 시각으로 자동 설정</stringProp>
        <intProp name="ThreadGroup.num_threads">1</intProp>
        <intProp name="ThreadGroup.ramp_time">1</intProp>
        <boolProp name="ThreadGroup.same_user_on_next_iteration">true</boolProp>
        <stringProp name="ThreadGroup.on_sample_error">continue</stringProp>
        <elementProp name="ThreadGroup.main_controller" elementType="LoopController" guiclass="LoopControlPanel" testclass="LoopController" testname="Loop Controller">
          <stringProp name="LoopController.loops">1</stringProp>
          <boolProp name="LoopController.continue_forever">false</boolProp>
        </elementProp>
      </SetupThreadGroup>
      <hashTree>
        <JSR223Sampler guiclass="TestBeanGUI" testclass="JSR223Sampler" testname="TS 초기화 (타임스탬프)" enabled="true">
          <stringProp name="scriptLanguage">groovy</stringProp>
          <stringProp name="script">if (!props.get(&quot;TS&quot;) || props.get(&quot;TS&quot;) == &quot;1&quot;) {
    props.put(&quot;TS&quot;, new Date().format(&quot;yyyyMMdd-HHmmss&quot;))
}
log.info(&quot;TS = &quot; + props.get(&quot;TS&quot;))</stringProp>
          <stringProp name="parameters"></stringProp>
          <stringProp name="filename"></stringProp>
          <stringProp name="cacheKey">false</stringProp>
        </JSR223Sampler>
        <hashTree/>
      </hashTree>
      <ThreadGroup guiclass="ThreadGroupGui" testclass="ThreadGroup" testname="[B-3] Hospital 집중 부하" enabled="true">
        <stringProp name="TestPlan.comments">파라미터 없는 전체 검색 + 근처 병원 집중 부하
GET /api/hospital/search (파라미터 없음): 전체 병원 반환 → 대용량 응답, Heap 증가 관찰
GET /api/hospital/nearby: Haversine CPU 부하 관찰
인증 불필요 (permitAll)</stringProp>
        <intProp name="ThreadGroup.num_threads">50</intProp>
        <intProp name="ThreadGroup.ramp_time">30</intProp>
        <longProp name="ThreadGroup.duration">300</longProp>
        <longProp name="ThreadGroup.delay">0</longProp>
        <boolProp name="ThreadGroup.same_user_on_next_iteration">true</boolProp>
        <boolProp name="ThreadGroup.scheduler">true</boolProp>
        <stringProp name="ThreadGroup.on_sample_error">continue</stringProp>
        <elementProp name="ThreadGroup.main_controller" elementType="LoopController" guiclass="LoopControlPanel" testclass="LoopController" testname="Loop Controller">
          <intProp name="LoopController.loops">-1</intProp>
          <boolProp name="LoopController.continue_forever">false</boolProp>
        </elementProp>
      </ThreadGroup>
      <hashTree>
        <HeaderManager guiclass="HeaderPanel" testclass="HeaderManager" testname="HTTP Header Manager" enabled="true">
          <collectionProp name="HeaderManager.headers">
            <elementProp name="" elementType="Header">
              <stringProp name="Header.name">Content-Type</stringProp>
              <stringProp name="Header.value">application/json</stringProp>
